attributes.background:
Cut number of constituencies to 325;
no MP's from Scotland, Wales or Ireland 
( they have their own bodies ) plus 1 for the speaker who should stand for election by the public and not represent any constituency or party. The Speaker should be free to deselect any MP who he deems to have behaved dishonourably and call a by-election. Free votes on all important issues ie Iraq War, EU Referendum, Immigration etc
